frames.caption: A woman stands gracefully under a starry night sky, wearing an ethereal gown that glows with intricate patterns of light. The dress appears to be alive, with luminous branches of light flowing through it, casting a magical aura around her. The moon shines brightly above, adding to the enchanting atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set outdoors at night, with a clear view of the star-filled sky and a bright moon. The woman is the focal point, standing amidst a snowy landscape, wearing a dress that seems to be illuminated from within, creating a surreal and mystical ambiance.

frames.caption: A woman stands gracefully on a snowy landscape under a starry night sky. Her dress glows with ethereal lights, blending with the serene winter scene. Snow-covered trees frame the background, enhancing the magical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a tranquil winter night with a woman in an illuminated gown standing amidst snow. The setting is peaceful and enchanting, with stars twinkling above and snow blanketing the ground.
